        <div1 type="summary">
            <p><add hand="#barker">Asking information about Texas and terms upon which land is granted.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            


<p><placeName>St Francisville</placeName> <date when="1821-11-22">November the 22nd 1921</date></p>
<p>Sir</p>

<p>I have some idea of moving to the <placeName>province of texes</placeName> to make a 
<placeName>settlement </placeName>in that country and wish to know the terms on which you
settle people in that province on your <placeName>grant</placeName>. I wish in the first place
to know how you expect to hold your land Secondly how much you
will give to each individual <persName>Settler</persName>, what are the productions of the
soil and what is the appearance with respect to health, I wish you
also to state when it [is] necessary for the settlement to be made, and
what part of the country I must go and who to apply to when there   it<pb n="434"/>
is probable there will be several small <persName>families </persName>of us will go together
if I like the prospect, be so good as to answer soon your obedient
servant</p>

<p><persName>Joseph T Montgomery</persName></p>
<p>[Addressed:] <persName>Mr Stephen F Austin </persName><placeName>New Orleans</placeName></p>


        </div1>
